id: act1_04_first_scene

prompt:
  The room dims and re-renders as a sunlit garden path. A wooden sign at the
  fork reads "Welcome. Take your time." Three small markers wait at the
  start of the path.

choice c_walk_with_npc:
  tendency: kindness
  text: Walk with the figure already on the path and match their pace.
  evidence: walked beside an NPC at their pace in the opening garden

choice c_survey_garden:
  tendency: control
  text: Stop and map the path's branches before stepping onto it.
  evidence: surveyed the opening garden's layout before stepping onto it

choice c_step_off_path:
  tendency: defiance
  text: Step off the marked path immediately and head into the long grass.
  evidence: stepped off the marked garden path immediately
